<p class="">Is that part of the policy of appeasement?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-c77fabe0-3e7b-46a6-94a0-3b2aa04d7e5b" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
