    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I was in the labour camps and I was told the wage is 2d. a day and that each man is given a quarter of a 1b. of white lard and no butter.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-6808022b-8b15-404e-bf97-d698ab7aa444" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-11-01/debates/41628fb5-99b8-421e-b2b4-4fd96d345da4/InternationalSituation#contribution-6808022b-8b15-404e-bf97-d698ab7aa444">
